cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ALPminer in your research, please cite it as below."
title: ALPminer
abstract: >-
  An open-source, resumable pipeline that mines atomic layer deposition (ALD)
  and atomic layer etching (ALE) process recipes from the published literature
  into AI-ready datasets, using the LLM provider of your choice through a
  no-code web dashboard.
